subject: Lacrosse
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Denver,  16th-ranked, defeated sixth-ranked Loyola of Maryland, 12-4, to win its first E.C.A.C. championship and the conference’s automatic bid to the N.C.A.A. tournament.
